org.egov.collection.integration.services

Class BillingIntegrationServiceStub

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.egov.collection.integration.services.BillingIntegrationServiceStub
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BillingIntegrationService

    public class BillingIntegrationServiceStub
extends Object
implements BillingIntegrationService
    This interface needs to be implemented by any billing application that integrates with the eGov collection system. For internal applications, the methods can use direct API calls. For external applications, the integration can be through web-service/REST calls. The convention to be followed: a bean named "collectionsInterface" needs to be available in the spring context. Service name is the name provided for the billing service in class.
